            "class": "",
            "text": "He called Jacob, therefore, and sent him to Padan-Aram to his mother's relations, with instructions to seek a wife there, and not among the daughters of Canaan, giving him at the same time the \"blessing of Abraham,\" i.e., the blessing of promise, which Abraham had repeatedly received from the Lord, but which is more especially recorded in ",
